    "note": "Hand-curated mirror of the migration files. Update after every migration so git diffs show schema changes without running PB. PB 0.23+ only auto-creates `id`; `created`/`updated` columns require an explicit `autodate` field. Per §7.1/§7.9, `match_events` and `match_audit` declare `created` autodate; other collections do not."
  },
